      <title>索马里分离地区选举反对派领导人为总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/breakaway-somalia-region-elects-opposition-leader-as-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名反对派领导人击败了现任总统穆塞·比希·阿卜迪，赢得了索马里兰半自治区的选举。]]></description>
