    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚可能恢复税收特赦以增加收入，扩大税基</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/indonesia-may-revive-tax-amnesty-to-lift-revenue-widen-tax-base</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚总统普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 领导的政府正在寻求增加国家收入和扩大税基的方法，印尼将于明年讨论恢复税收赦免计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/indonesia-may-revive-tax-amnesty-to-lift-revenue-widen-tax-base</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 06:35:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本自民党任命前部长山极和为芯片沙皇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/japan-s-ruling-party-names-former-minister-yamagiwa-as-chip-czar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本执政党任命山极大四郎为其半导体推广委员会的新任主席，并建立了新机制来增加对这一关键行业的资助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/japan-s-ruling-party-names-former-minister-yamagiwa-as-chip-czar</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:55:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>紧张局势缓和 中国寻求恢复与印度的直航</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/china-seeks-to-resume-direct-flights-with-india-as-tensions-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国外交部长王毅表示，中国希望恢复与印度的直航，因为经过四年的边界争端僵局之后，这两个亚洲邻国之间的紧张局势正在缓和。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/china-seeks-to-resume-direct-flights-with-india-as-tensions-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:32:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
