    <item>
      <title>分析人士称欧洲可能需要 7200 亿美元国防开支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/europe-may-need-720-billion-in-defense-spending-analysts-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社研究报告称，欧洲主要国家可能需要增加国防开支，以应对俄罗斯入侵乌克兰的挑战，以及唐纳德·特朗普出任总统后美国支持率可能下降的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/europe-may-need-720-billion-in-defense-spending-analysts-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称一辆越野车冲撞学校外人群</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/china-says-suv-plowed-into-crowd-of-people-outside-a-school</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国称，一辆越野车冲撞一所小学的人群，造成多人受伤 — — 这一事件正值中国因一系列暴力袭击而陷入紧张状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/china-says-suv-plowed-into-crowd-of-people-outside-a-school</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 03:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国家庭债务上季度涨幅创 2021 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/south-korea-s-household-debt-rose-most-last-quarter-since-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上季度，韩国家庭债务增幅达到三年来的最高水平，突显出韩国央行直到上个月才改变政策的趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-19/south-korea-s-household-debt-rose-most-last-quarter-since-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港国安法最长刑期：戴耀廷被判十年有期徒刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/hong-kong-to-sentence-45-activists-in-biggest-security-law-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港法院判处前民主倡导者戴耀廷 10 年监禁，这是中国国家安全法判处的最长刑期，此举可能会进一步遏制香港这个金融中心的异议人士，并招致西方政府的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/hong-kong-to-sentence-45-activists-in-biggest-security-law-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 23:39:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
